law.history: Repealed 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 109, sec. 40, effective March 30, 1992; amended 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 194, sec. 2. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 296, sec. 17, effective July 15, 1986. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 346, sec. 14.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/14/92). This section was amended by the 1992 Regular Session of the General Assembly and also repealed. Pursuant to KRS 446.260, the repeal prevails.
